response.original_title: Dua Lipa - The Beat Before (Wembley Stadium)
response.overview: 2 SOLD OUT NIGHTS AT WEMBLEY STADIUM!! the most special, unforgettable shows I’ve ever done!!!  I’m overwhelmed with gratitude. For this journey. For every single person who’s stood by me, believed in me, sung with me, danced with me, and shared in this dream. Thank you from the bottom of my heart to the incredible team on stage and behind the scenes who pour so much love and work into making this possible. I truly couldn’t have done this without you.  Wembley, you have my heart. Forever.  Directed by: Becky Garner  Produced by: Tara Bartlett  DOP: Toby Leary Production Company: Lowkey Films / Radical22 Productions  Management: Radical Management - Dugi Lipa, Sofia Gold, Joel Quartey, Jess Spink, Maisy Nicholson, Olivia Moss, Rae Hayden & Nat Cooper.  Record Label: Warner Records Creative Commissioner: Imran Malik Lowkey Films Executive Producers: Alexa Haywood & Connor O’Hara Radical22 Productions Executive Producers: Dugi Lipa & Peter Abbott
